dc.title: Congressman Jim Walsh, 25th Congressional District of New York State - Homepage
dc.description: Congressman Jim Walsh represents New York State in the U.S. House of Representatives as a member of the Committee on Appropriations. His district includes Onondaga County, northern Cayuga County, Wayne County, and the northeastern portion of Monroe County.
